data.description: Welcome to this charming 5 bed/3 bath traditional home located in the desirable city of Lawrenceville. The two-story entrance foyer is flanked by a formal dining room and the office/den, and the spacious main floor offers a seamless flow throughout.  Fireside family room is the ideal space for relaxing and entertaining guests. The kitchen features stained cabinets and updated appliances, two pantries, a breakfast bar, an eat-in kitchen, and offers a great view to the family room.  A guest bedroom and an updated full bath with a shower/tub combo round out the main floor and plenty of counter space. Upper level features the Primary Suite with vaulted ceilings, a double vanity, separate shower, soaking tub, a walk-in closet, and an additional closet. Three spacious bedrooms share the full bath, ensuring that everyone has plenty of space and privacy. Outside, the backyard offers plenty of green space and storage shed! You'll love spending time outside in the sunshine or under the stars.  The location couldn't be better with easy access to Lawrenceville, Suwanee, and Duluth as well as highways 316, I85, and 985! Don't miss out on the opportunity to turn this house into your dream home. Schedule a showing today and get ready to start creating new memories in this wonderful Lawrenceville home!
